description: Kricketina Kylie came to the Kanto region to try to find a Pinsir. Goh tried to help her find a Pinsir but it ended up having to battle against Team Rocket. After fighting off Team Rocket, a wild Pinsir appeared and he caught it as Kricketina Kylie was caught in a net. She traded her Heracross to Goh for this Pinsir.
name: Kailios (Koromi)
